# Hexalith.EventStore — lychee link checker exclusions
# One regex pattern per line

# Localhost/loopback URLs (quickstart uses localhost:8080, localhost:8180)
^https?://localhost(:\d+)?
^https?://127\.0\.0\.1(:\d+)?
^https?://\[::1\](:\d+)?

# Example/placeholder domains
^https?://example\.com
^https?://example\.invalid
